spanGrp.span: rō enten yel ru lam bulbul ōr
everyone was working, they were planting cabbage
enten selanga ru lam kee , ru lam bya kabis
and I went and cleared one of mine
a nō nam an bulu sok ngo hol muru
then I cleaned (it), I haven't cleaned it all yet
rō nam bulu , natlo bul fini bwe
sok ōr lonōr mwee tiirbonok moro
I will just return again, go, I will just go and finish cleaning
enab bwiri ko lili mon van , enab bwiri an bul fini
I will wash the area that I have cleaned already
ru nam kai rō nam bulu ru bur rō mu
it is growing now and I am washing i(t)
myumyul ru ngele rō ru nam kai
as I will plant my cabbage in that place
ben go enab bya ak fyaar van nōr go ren
and I will plant water taro with (it)
the cabbage whic I am planting, cabbage
fyaar go ru nam bya , kabis
from the cyclone, which they gave
ne lengmwiaal go yel lar sengene
